  "detailed_description": "<strong>Darkly Darkness</strong> is a straightforward 2D action-platformer game centered around a boy's mission to save the planet from invading aliens. However, he soon discovers that there are more of them than he anticipated, and they're larger and far more dangerous than he ever imagined. Will he learn about this threat in time, or will it be too late?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945370/extras/47a8ecb79522e01782abe8ea5b83aa41.poster.avif?t=1722546099\" width=620 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945370/extras/47a8ecb79522e01782abe8ea5b83aa41.webm?t=1722546099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945370/extras/47a8ecb79522e01782abe8ea5b83aa41.mp4?t=1722546099\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>Game Features:</i><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 8 unique carefully crafted dangerous bosses;<br></li><li> 5 different weapons including a shotgun;<br></li><li> good simple story;<br></li><li> stunning particle effects;</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945370/extras/6c976a3572966509bf374a72f02a11e0.avif?t=1722546099\" width=620 height=134 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945370/extras/6230bda38cea58bdfa56d961ef6aab63.avif?t=1722546099\" width=620 height=134 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945370/extras/2c42eac64c74c212dcc5f502d359f00c.avif?t=1722546099\" width=620 height=134 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945370/extras/bee611648370104dfffca12bf5d7767c.avif?t=1722546099\" width=620 height=134 /></span><br><br>Calling all fans of 2D action-platformers! Dive into the adrenaline-pumping excitement of our game tailor-made just for you.",
